TY  - JOUR
TI  - On the Optimality of Central Places
AU  - Quinzii, Martine
AU  - Thisse, Jacques-François
AB  - [Using the Eaton and Lipsey model, we show that a hierarchical system of central places is socially optimal: firms having less frequent purchases are clustered with firms having more frequent purchases in any configuration minimizing total transport and production costs.]
